               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ALLEN-<rs id="t18180617-118-verdict662" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180617-118-verdict662" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
